  Hoe5-siong2 i ti7 Tiong-oh8 e5 si5-tai7, ti7 un7-tong7-kai3 cho3 kha-kiu5 e5 soan2-chhiu2, eng-kai tioh8 sin-the2 kian7-khong, hoan2- tng2 the2-chit soe-jiok8, che kiaN-liau2 tui3 in-khin5 houN3-hak8 sou2 ti3. Si3 goeh8 27 e5 an-hioh-jit8 e5-hng, sian-siN hu-hu7 nng7- lang5 lai5 goan2 tau sio-tham3, kau3 11 tiam2 chiah tng2-khi3, to bo5 khoaN3-tioh8 Tek- chiong Sian-siN u7 koh-iuN7 e5 thai3-tou7, kau3 5 goeh8 chhe-ji7 me5 7 tiam2 chhut, khi3- kng2 hoat peN7, liam5-piN tng2 khi3 chou2-ke. I khia7-khi2 ti7 chit-liap8 te7-kiu5 chheN u7 38 ni5 ku2. Hian7-si5 i e5 ka-chok8 iau2 u7 10 lang5 toa3 ti7 chit8-e5 kia3-liu5 te7, u7 pe7-bo2, hu7- jin5-lang5, nng7-e5 ta-pou gin2-na2, si3-e5 cha- bou2 gin2-na2, kap chit8-e5 sio2-moe7. Tui3 chit ho7 keng2-gu7, in e5 sim-lai7 chaiN2-iuN7, lang5 lang5 long2 chai, m7-bian2 kong2. ChhiaN2 lan2 tong5-cheng5, kiu5 chu5-ai3 e5 ThiN Pe7 chiong I e5 peng5-an lai5 chhiong-moa2 in e5 sim, e7 hou7 in ng3-bang7 Siong7-te3 e5 eng5- kng lai5 hoaN-hoaN hi2-hi2. 
